race.description: Congrats Tim Mason Krc Maiden Plate
race.comment: SORT CHA MESS (3) is a son of Tassort out of Shuwaamekh who was sold for AUD $4,000 (Magic Millions 2023 Gold Coast National Weanling Sale). Impressed in winning a trial at Gatton with today's rider Les Tilley aboard. Expected to go well. PIPPIE POMAR (10) has been racing in great heart with two top-three finishes on end, the latest a third over 860m at Gatton when she was in the firing line all the way. Likely improver with strong prospects. MISHANI HERCULES (2) was in contention on the turn and finished second last time over 800m at this track when resuming from a spell, beaten 4.5 lengths. Will trim down second-up. Placed to advantage so expect another bold run. GOING MY WAY (9) draws the inside marble and may run a race while fresh.
